of a student visa.
"PHE visa" means either:
  (a)  a Subclass 485 (Temporary Graduate) visa in the Post - Study Work stream or the Post -
Higher Education Work stream; or
  (b)  a Subclass 485 (Temporary Graduate) visa in the Replacement stream held by a person who
previously held a Subclass 485 (Temporary Graduate) visa in the Post - Study Work stream.
